- Sample fees: $50–$200 per design (deducted from first order in most cases)
- MOQ: 30–100 pieces per design at most Thai specialist manufacturers
- Unit production cost: Varies significantly by design complexity, materials, and stones. Budget for your first quote to include a request for unit price at your target MOQ.
